{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "learnfyra-complete-api-2026",
    "name": "Learnfyra Complete API — All 41 Endpoints",
    "description": "Comprehensive test collection for Learnfyra API. Covers all 41 implemented endpoints across 11 feature groups for local dev and AWS Lambda deployments.\n\n**Setup Instructions:**\n1. Set `baseUrl` collection variable to your environment (http://localhost:3000 for local)\n2. Run Auth folder first — Register then Login. Login scripts auto-capture tokens into collection variables.\n3. Run other folders in order; each section uses IDs captured by previous sections.\n4. For local testing: ensure `npm run dev` is running on port 3000.\n\n**Environment URLs:**\n- Local: http://localhost:3000\n- Dev: https://api.dev.learnfyra.com\n- QA/Staging: https://api.qa.learnfyra.com\n- Prod: https://api.learnfyra.com\n\n**Auth Modes:**\n- Local: email/password via mock adapter (bcrypt + JSON files)\n- AWS (all envs): hybrid — email/password + Google OAuth via Cognito",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",       "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "studentToken",  "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "teacherToken",  "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "worksheetId",   "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "classId",       "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "studentId",     "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "childId",       "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "certificateId", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "questionId",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "inviteCode",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "description": "Authentication endpoints — no token required (endpoints 1-8). Run Register then Login to populate tokens. refresh, forgot-password, and reset-password work in all environments.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Student)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token)  { pm.collectionVariables.set('studentToken', jsonData.token); }",
                  "if (jsonData.userId) { pm.collectionVariables.set('studentId', jsonData.userId); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Passw0rd123!\",\n  \"role\": \"student\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Test Student\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Teacher)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('teacherToken', jsonData.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Passw0rd123!\",\n  \"role\": \"teacher\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Test Teacher\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Student)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token)  { pm.collectionVariables.set('studentToken', jsonData.token); }",
                  "if (jsonData.userId) { pm.collectionVariables.set('studentId', jsonData.userId); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Passw0rd123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Teacher)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('teacherToken', jsonData.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Passw0rd123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', jsonData.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Passw0rd123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{studentToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{}" },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('studentToken', jsonData.token); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"<paste-refresh-token-here>\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Forgot Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forgot-password"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Reset Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"<reset-token-from-email>\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewPassw0rd123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "OAuth Start (Google)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"redirectUri\": \"{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/google\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/oauth/google"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "OAuth Callback (Google)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/google?code=sample-code&state=sample-state",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "callback", "google"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "code",  "value": "sample-code" },
                { "key": "state", "value": "sample-state" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Worksheet",
      "description": "Worksheet lifecycle: Generate (JWT required) → Solve (JWT required) → Submit (JWT required) → Download (unauthenticated).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Generate Worksheet",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.metadata && jsonData.metadata.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('worksheetId', jsonData.metadata.id);",
                  "  console.log('worksheetId captured: ' + jsonData.metadata.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{studentToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"grade\": 4,\n  \"subject\": \"Math\",\n  \"topic\": \"Factors and Multiples\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"Easy\",\n  \"questionCount\": 10,\n  \"format\": \"HTML\",\n  \"includeAnswerKey\": true,\n  \"generationMode\": \"auto\",\n  \"provenanceLevel\": \"summary\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/generate"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Solve Page (No Answers)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{studentToken}}" }],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/solve/{{worksheetId}}"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit Answers & Score",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  console.log('Score: ' + body.totalScore + '/' + body.totalPoints + ' (' + body.percentage + '%)');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{studentToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"worksheetId\": \"{{worksheetId}}\",\n  \"answers\": [\n    { \"number\": 1, \"answer\": \"B\" },\n    { \"number\": 2, \"answer\": \"True\" },\n    { \"number\": 3, \"answer\": \"42\" },\n    { \"number\": 4, \"answer\": \"B\" },\n    { \"number\": 5, \"answer\": \"sample answer\" },\n    { \"number\": 6, \"answer\": \"20\" },\n    { \"number\": 7, \"answer\": \"sample answer\" },\n    { \"number\": 8, \"answer\": \"True\" },\n    { \"number\": 9, \"answer\": \"B\" },\n    { \"number\": 10, \"answer\": \"42\" }\n  ],\n  \"timeTaken\": 600,\n  \"timed\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/submit"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Download Worksheet File",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/download?key=worksheets/2026/04/01/{{worksheetId}}/worksheet.html",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "download"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "key", "value": "worksheets/2026/04/01/{{worksheetId}}/worksheet.html" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
